---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="mt-12 sm:mt-16 mb-4 sm:mb-6 mx-2 sm:mx-3 md:mx-6">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl rounded-2xl sm:rounded-[1.75rem] bg-[var(--color-cocoa)] text-[var(--color-sugar)] px-5 sm:px-6 md:px-10 py-8 sm:py-10 md:py-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-5 sm:gap-6">
    <div>
      <p class="font-display italic text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-2">
        Delicateses Doña Rosa
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/75 max-w-md leading-relaxed">
        Galletas, tortas y postres hechos con cariño en Venezuela. Pedidos por WhatsApp.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-white/60">
      © {year} Delicateses Doña Rosa
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
